24/Apr/2017 04:23 PM;smielcarek;In case of the line series chart where dimension is defined as, for example: debitCredit|date, the date ranges (minDate and maxDate) are calculated incorrectly. The reason for this is that in this case we have two dimensions and records are sorted by the first dimesion, which is debitCredit. This is determined by the fragment of the code responsible for creating dimensions:

{code:JavaScript}
asDimensions[index] = (ndx_data.dimension(function (d) {
    if (d[aDimensions[0]] !== null) {
      dimSeries1 = d[aDimensions[0]];
    }
    if (d[aDimensions[1]] !== null) {
      dimSeries2 = d[aDimensions[1]];
    }
return [dimSeries1, dimSeries2];
}
