Additionally then, seriesAccessor and keyAccessor (defined in series chart) need to be also changed from:

{code:JavaScript}
.seriesAccessor(function (d) {return d.key[0]; })
.keyAccessor(function (d) {return d.key[1]; })
{code}

into:

{code:JavaScript}
.seriesAccessor(function (d) {return d.key[1]; })
